
in this workshop i learned
 * what is ansible
 *  principals of ansible (playbook, inventory ,role and var precedence)
 * handling few ansible modules like file, stat, template(jinja2), lineinfile and apt
 * create roles and playbooks in master ansible host  to install apache server, install LAMP stack, add/update files in target servers

technical environment
 one master ansible in one docker container
 multiple target server in multiple docker containers
 those containers are deployer using docker-compose.yml 




